Package: data.cms.gov
Title: CMS Provider Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the CMS Provider Data API. Access 233+
    healthcare datasets including hospitals, nursing homes, dialysis facilities,
    home health agencies, and quality measures. Auto-paginates large queries.
